{"tid":427034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際零支持］加泰獨派內部釀分裂","createTime":"2017-10-07T07:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T08:54:26.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"58328b2b56b6f517d269c1bdd510bce8b037d885","tid":427034,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T07:22:11.000Z","msg":"西班牙加泰羅尼亞正在蘊釀獨立之際，卻傳出「獨派」內部陷入分裂的消息。自治政府的商貿部官員在報章撰文指，要求政府反思現行的策略是否可行及後果。 <br />\n<br />\n該名官員為維拉（Santi Vila），他在當地報章《阿拉報》發表評論文章，促請親獨立陣營反思單方面宣布獨立，能否達到預期中的效果以及其所帶來的後果。前自治政府主席馬斯向英國《金融時報》表示：「普伊格登莫尼特不應想着如何宣布獨立，而是要想應要如何達到。」 <br />\n<br />\n有學者分析指，加泰自治政府已漸漸失去國際社會的同情及目光，若然他們宣布獨立，馬德里政府或會乘機以更強硬手段對付自治政府。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171007/mobile/bknint-20171007143022807-1007_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171007%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20171007143022807-1007_17011_001.html&d=SWnDTpVlGp35FCDRvsOo89ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=75d199ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171007/mobile/bknint-20171007143022807-1007_17011_001.html</a><br />\n沒有歐盟，聯合國，美國撐腰，已經攪唔起"},{"pid":"90e521fd7ef8a51a273d476488934df1cbbb179e","tid":427034,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T07:28:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=SWnDTpVlGp35FCDRvsOo89ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=133b67cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"dbdaccc0d413916484cef1675c68c64bd98f49b8","tid":427034,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=SWnDTpVlGp35FCDRvsOo89ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=133b67cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"b40d379c9f83da11936771e36ef7aad49d954aae","tid":427034,"uid":41116,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾東方又cut 前cut 後<br />\nHe added: &ldquo;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">We have won the right to be an independent country.[</span>/b] The question now is how do we exercise that right, and here obviously there are decisions to be taken. And these decisions must have one objective in mind: [b]<span style=\"color: red;\">this is not just about proclaiming independence but about actually becoming an independent country</strong>.&rdquo;</span>"},{"pid":"b0dcbb4f76e42a00f6b6c8ac906ded3f822a9bd1","tid":427034,"uid":35774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T07:44:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">on.99</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f641de84246f74b3ee614c75b8280c9571bc92","tid":427034,"uid":22858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T07:53:11.000Z","msg":"樓主陰險"},{"pid":"f60442626ea459553259ba1819826f40958ff2dd","tid":427034,"uid":19557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"樓豬好賤"},{"pid":"49f7ed551d0d09ff6257c8db8747ae7749c0b33e","tid":427034,"uid":41695,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/162303_b81ae73c2e47fe31b340bb8483270bef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F162303_b81ae73c2e47fe31b340bb8483270bef.jpg&h=8eaa0e4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bc043d312e8a9a47078e68da20ac2d86609a5b6","tid":427034,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"因報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clow